# Default: normalize all text files to LF on checkout, everywhere. This repo is
# authored on Windows with core.autocrlf=true; without this a fresh clone or CI
# on Windows rewrites LF->CRLF and breaks byte-exact tests (scoring determinism,
# HTML byte-identity). Existing blobs are already LF, so this is churn-free.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Specific overrides come AFTER the glob (gitattributes is last-match-wins).

# The marketplace census MUST be verbatim bytes: it contains intentional bare-LF
# newlines inside quoted multiline taglines that tests assert on byte-for-byte.
# `binary` (= -text -diff) disables ALL line-ending conversion.
data/okx-marketplace-census-2026-07-10.csv binary

# Runtime data artifacts (gitignored anyway) — never convert.
*.db      binary
*.sqlite3 binary
